title: At least 12 dead after 6.5-magnitude earthquake strikes off coast of Ecuador
description: At least 12 people are dead after a 6.5-magnitude earthquake occurred off the coast of Ecuador Saturday, authorities said.

title: EXCLUSIVE: Pence says Trump arrest would be 'a politically charged prosecution'
description: During an exclusive sit-down interview, Pence said he's "taken aback" at the prospect of a possible indictment and arrest of former President Donald Trump.

title: Frozen organic strawberries recalled over possible link to hepatitis A outbreak
description: The U.S. Food and Drug Administration is investigating an outbreak of hepatitis A infections that may be linked to frozen organic strawberries.

title: Mysterious streaks of light seen in the sky over California

title: Earthquake in Ecuador kills at least 1, causes wide damage

title: Wyoming governor signs measure prohibiting abortion pills

title: Fairleigh Dickinson stuns No. 1 seed Purdue in March Madness
description: Fairleigh Dickinson became the second No. 16 seed in history to win an NCAA Tournament game, stunning top-seeded Purdue 63-58 behind 19 points from Sean Moore and a relentless, hustling defense

title: SVB execs sold millions in company stock in lead up to collapse, disclosures show
description: Former SVB President and CEO Greg Becker sold over $3.5 million of his company stock holdings on Feb. 27, according to a disclosure made to the SEC.
